{"tid":1616724,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【石硤尾名店】被指藍絲拒接待黑衫 品香樓老闆回應撐學生：無能政府造成這局面","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T18:44:39.000Z","uid":51583,"like":30,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8023d492e43a80b58c67fabd3b3938cb8e268af7","tid":1616724,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191003/60113898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191003%2F60113898&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCElQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=505f441a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191003%2F60113898&h=d73a07e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191003/60113898</a><br />\n<br />\n有網民指10月1日參與國慶日大遊行後，身穿黑衣進入位於石硤尾南山村的名店「品香樓」用膳，打開背包時被店員見到裝備（gear），被拒入內。帖文引發熱烈討論，多數人指品香樓做了多年城大和浸大學生的生意，竟然不支持學生和今次運動，發起抵制品香樓。<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】槍擊學生重重疑團未解 警方今不舉行記者會<br />\n<br />\n記者今日（3號）來到品香樓，負責人Sam Wong指事件並非屬實，為沒有根據的指控。「我也有看閉路電視，並有翻看再前一晚閉路電視，也沒有特別情況發生。查問每個員工也說沒有，她們不會這樣趕人走，食客帶甚麼不關她們事。這個指控到底存不存在？如果真有其事，我願意和當事人解釋道歉。」<br />\n <br />\nSam更坦言自己支持學生，指「覺得學生好勇敢偉大，犧牲自己該有的暑假，為香港人爭取民主和自由。」他續指，「是無能的政府造成這樣局面；叫你回應訴求，你遊花園；說和市民對話，每人只得3分鐘。對話不是這樣的&mdash;&mdash; 如果你問我，我也是說，學生和香港人加油！」"},{"pid":"7fdcebc56af995ccb6b6e9c34020f027eae4f142","tid":1616724,"uid":98242,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:51:21.000Z","msg":"收皮"},{"pid":"2847009f72a63b76b1b24868afca7974f867acbb","tid":1616724,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"叫佢講返16粒字先啦"},{"pid":"f2f1fbd23ef85b826bb8508f1a0cc1d84c316464","tid":1616724,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:54:11.000Z","msg":"其實黑警有冇打算向印尼記者道歉？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616651</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b8e5cf3179c9a9426c332232d96d4c1cfa960b18","tid":1616724,"uid":252660,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"唔撚信 藍到仆街"},{"pid":"8e305d3b04aa4ca6721e0e4882da8b937650623c","tid":1616724,"uid":52960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"今日都好多客"},{"pid":"3d004c698e881086fddc3362448dde9c317b91df","tid":1616724,"uid":126046,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"Too late<br />\nKeep fucking"},{"pid":"4d826530bf103566cedc656ddec6c1f09f85d0a6","tid":1616724,"uid":37740,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n起屋企嗌口號都要比你班放工既職員指住兇 垃圾"},{"pid":"655e15d32f6549092e7e76d6f8ab815e029b6aa7","tid":1616724,"uid":287211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:18:58.000Z","msg":"收皮"},{"pid":"64e1d7a766fa24160d0ad167b9a5554e28beac45","tid":1616724,"uid":188482,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"扮咩 見龍門好生意就個個爭住扮黃同割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040904a505287c263270d51cc5085635c582f562","tid":1616724,"uid":329466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"嗌番句口號 俾人連儂就信喇"},{"pid":"bfab13b2de28f92c0a173e8c9ec6acd53baedf35","tid":1616724,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T20:42:21.000Z","msg":"扮黃？"},{"pid":"89f65e7a8937469aa18bfc53e1ba5439a9e7a8de","tid":1616724,"uid":215700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"既然講到咁 咪觀察下囉<br />\n唔駛當佢黃店咁衝去食<br />\n不過都唔駛當佢係藍店咁罷食<br />\n比下機會堆餐廳表達支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0fee7d4b4e6b81f12a1bfceaba41eb802ad451","tid":161672